{"id":144,"date":"2017-07-20T08:12:22","date_gmt":"2017-07-20T08:12:22","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/hoodbuilder.dev\/?page_id=144"},"modified":"2023-11-18T19:58:20","modified_gmt":"2023-11-18T19:58:20","slug":"remodeling","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/restaurant-services\/remodeling\/","title":{"rendered":"Restaurant Remodeling"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1500556319702{background-color: #eeeeec !important;}&#8221;][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-2 vc_col-lg-8 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-10&#8243;]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e55151da6b\" data-id=\"685e55151da6b\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"big-para-blue\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hood Builder is the premier <a href=\"\/restaurant-construction-remodeling-in-denver\/\">restaurant remodeling service<\/a> that works with clients throughout Denver, Colorado. For nearly thirty years, we have been providing restaurant owners with the best exterior and interior design they require to please their loyal customers.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"tel:+1-303-777-7720\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px 10px 20px; background-color: #0067ab;\">Free Quote (303-777-7720)<\/a><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e55151da86\" data-id=\"685e55151da86\" data-height=\"60\" data-height-mobile=\"40\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"40\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e55151da97\" data-id=\"685e55151da97\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-7 vc_col-md-7&#8243;][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There is no project too big or small for our restaurant remodeling contractors. We can help you plan the perfect restaurant makeover, draw up plans, and handle all the contracting and construction from the ground up.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>You Don\u2019t Have to Remodel on Your Own\u00a0<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/restaurant-services\/design\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">restaurant remodel and redesign<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> may seem like a daunting task but imagine the peace of mind you will enjoy when you finally see your vision of the ideal makeover come to life.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here is what our restaurant remodeling professionals have to offer you.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Experience:\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">We have been remodeling top restaurants for name-brand establishments for over 25 years. We are known throughout the Denver areas for providing makeovers that make business owners proud to re-open after the renovations have been completed. You could be one of them.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Expertise:\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">Our restaurant design-build specialists have worked with all types of restaurants and can accommodate your restaurant remodeling plans. We can make suggestions that will make your ideas really wow your audience, and we can draw up plans based on your vision alone. When you work with us, we make sure to include you in all major decision making to ensure you\u2019re always happy with the final product.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Attention-to-Detail:\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">We take time to do things properly the first time around. When we complete the final restaurant remodel walk-through, you will see how detailed our construction can be. We go above and beyond because we want your restaurant to be successful and for your customers to be wowed.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Transparent Communication:\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">We walk you through the entire process of the restaurant remodel and design project. From bidding and pre-construction to cleaning up after the project is done, we keep you updated every step of the way.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Quality Guarantee: <\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">You are going to be happy with your restaurant interior and exterior design, we guarantee it. We also ensure that your project will be done by the deadline while adhering to your budget.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The bottom line is that you can relax when you choose Hood Builder. From restaurant design to the construction aspect and all steps in-between, we can show you that remodeling your restaurant doesn\u2019t have to be such a complicated affair.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>Restaurant Planning &amp; the Finished Project<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We want to hear your vision of the perfect restaurant. Listening to your plans will allow us to get right to work. Our trained and experienced <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/restaurant-services\/construction\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">restaurant construction team<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and designers will draw up designs for you to approve, then our restaurant construction team can make your vision come alive for your customers to enjoy.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once you approve the plans, our construction team will work behind-the-scenes while you help customers, or we can work after-hours. We work on your schedule to ensure business runs as usual while we expedite the restaurant construction process as much as we can.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>Years of Restaurant Remodeling Experience<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our customers return to us because we remodel restaurants that customers want to visit. When you decide to engage in a restaurant remodel, you face a ton of obstacles, many of them expensive. This isn\u2019t a time to tackle the project all on your own.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We guarantee that our professional team of architects, interior designers, and construction professionals will work beside you, helping to make your restaurant the best in town.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>Schedule Your Restaurant Remodel Today<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Call and tell us about your restaurant remodeling plan. We will work with you to plan your design and bring it to fruition. From small projects to turn-key makeovers, we can take care of all your restaurant design-build projects from A to Z.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We can handle any sized job, no matter if you have a <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/restaurant-build-up-experts-will-save-you-money-time-and-trouble-during-your-restaurant-design-process\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">franchise remodeling project<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> or a fine dining construction job. We can even handle fast food, coffee shops, and more.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you have an idea for the perfect restaurant remodeling project, we have you covered. As you will soon see, our remodeled restaurants quickly become local faves.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ready to get started? For a full and honest quote, <\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/contact-us\/\"><b>contact Hood Builder<\/b><\/a><b> today.<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"tel:+1-303-777-7720\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px 10px 20px; background-color: #0067ab;\">Free Quote (303-777-7720)<\/a><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-1 vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-4&#8243;][vc_wp_custommenu nav_menu=&#8221;9&#8243; el_class=&#8221;wps-sidebar-related-links&#8221; title=&#8221;Related Links&#8221;]<div class=\"templatera_shortcode\"><div id=\"\" class=\"wps-row-container vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" ><div class=\"container wps-vc-container\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div\n        class=\"sidebar-widget-button-wrap \">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button\">\n        <a href=\"\/services\/restaurant-services\/\" title=\"Restaurant Services\">\n\n            <div id=\"wps-sidebar-btn-362238\" class=\"sidebar-widget-button-details\">\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button-text\">\n                    <p>Restaurant Services<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-arrow\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/themes\/wps-hoodbuilder\/assets\/images\/icon-arrow-sidebar-services.svg\" alt=\"\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div\n        class=\"sidebar-widget-button-wrap \">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/fire-suppression-systems\/\" title=\"Fire Protection\">\n\n            <div id=\"wps-sidebar-btn-171631\" class=\"sidebar-widget-button-details\">\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button-text\">\n                    <p>Fire Protection<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-arrow\"